<subSubSection pageId="38" pageNumber="39" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1436,1079,1556]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,361,1343,1369]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Distribution:</emphasis>
Formerly known from 
<collectingCountry box="[649,758,1344,1370]" name="Morocco" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Morocco</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[773,878,1344,1370]" name="Gibraltar" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Gibraltar</collectingCountry>
and the Spanish province of Cadiz (
<bibRefCitation author="Bosmans, R." pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="173 - 191" refId="ref42524" refString="Bosmans, R. (2006 b) Contribution to the knowledge of the Linyphiidae of the Maghreb. Part X. New data on Lepthyphantes Menge (sensu lato) species (Araneae, Linyphiidae). Belgian Journal of Zoology, 136, 173 - 191." type="journal article" year="2006">Bosmans 2006b</bibRefCitation>
) and cited here for the first time from 
<collectingCountry box="[676,775,1381,1407]" name="Portugal" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Portugal</collectingCountry>
in several localities in the southern province 
<collectingRegion box="[1307,1364,1381,1407]" country="Portugal" name="Faro" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Faro</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1436,1079,1556]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,366,1418,1444]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
Habitat 
<typeStatus box="[302,360,1418,1444]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">type</typeStatus>
:
</emphasis>
The species can occur in different habitats, from pine forests, marshes, borders of rivers to margins of cultivated fields.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1436,1079,1556]" box="[198,885,1493,1519]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,338,1493,1519]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Phenology:</emphasis>
Adults were collected from February to April.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1436,1079,1556]" box="[151,638,1530,1556]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,638,1530,1556]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
[
<taxonomicName authority="(Simon, 1884)" baseAuthorityName="Simon" baseAuthorityYear="1884" box="[161,629,1530,1556]" class="Arachnida" family="Linyphiidae" genus="Palliduphantes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cernuus">
